<figureCitation id="136E2BF55559FFB550D0B856FCBAFCE2" box="[736,768,847,873]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="45.[189,232,1857,1883]" captionTargetBox="[194,1392,525,1818]" captionTargetId="figure-61@45.[189,1398,513,1818]" captionTargetPageId="45" captionText="Fig. 22. Earophanta serrata (Semenov, 1893), genitalia (ZIN). A. Tegmen of aedeagus, ventrally. B. Ditto, dorsally. C. Ditto, laterally. D. Median lobe, ventrally. E. Ditto, dorsally. F. Ditto, laterally. G. Spiculum gastrale. H. ♂, inner sternite VIII. I. ♀, inner sternite VIII and spiculum ventrale. J. ♀, ovipositor, ventrally. K. Ditto, dorsally. L. Ditto, laterally. Not to scale. Abbreviations: see Material and methods." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6419489" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6419489/files/figure.png" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">22</figureCitation>
